<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1437,1226,1505]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1371,1397]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Remarks.</emphasis>
The specimens examined were identified based on the description and illustrations by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nielson, M. W." box="[1262,1432,1371,1397]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 318" refId="ref38619" refString="Nielson, M. W. (1982) A revision of the subfamily Coelidiinae (Homoptera: Cicadellidae) IV. Coelidiini. Pacific Insects Monograph, 38, 1 - 318." type="journal article" year="1982">Nielson (1982)</bibRefCitation>
. The species was recorded earlier from 
<collectingCountry box="[584,654,1407,1433]" name="China" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">China</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[665,774,1407,1433]" name="Myanmar" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[828,931,1407,1433]" name="Thailand" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Thailand</collectingCountry>
. 
<collectingCountry box="[941,999,1407,1433]" name="India" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">India</collectingCountry>
is a new record. Specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[1379,1437,1407,1433]" name="India" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">India</collectingCountry>
differ by the following features: aedeagal shaft process reaching near midlength of the shaft with many spines (&gt;10) (
<figureCitation box="[160,268,1479,1505]" captionStart="FIGURES 36" captionStartId="71.[151,264,1977,2002]" captionTargetBox="[201,1411,189,1949]" captionTargetId="figure@71.[159,1427,166,1957]" captionTargetPageId="71" captionText="FIGURES 36 A–H. Olidiana perculta (Distant), male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C&amp;D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366616/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Fig. 36 B</figureCitation>
); pygofer with small, digitate, caudoventral process (
<figureCitation box="[864,975,1479,1505]" captionStart="FIGURES 36" captionStartId="71.[151,264,1977,2002]" captionTargetBox="[201,1411,189,1949]" captionTargetId="figure@71.[159,1427,166,1957]" captionTargetPageId="71" captionText="FIGURES 36 A–H. Olidiana perculta (Distant), male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C&amp;D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366616/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Fig. 36 H</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
